== Instance "access" permission ==

Some of this access might be mentioned on other pages. Users might come here first.

* Access permission can be blocked by 1h if you are kicked/banned.
* Access can be blocked do to content filtering[[File:Instance_Access_Permission.png|thumb]]
* Access can be blocked to goup instances, missing Group Instance join permission if group any group instance type
* Access can be blocked to goup instances, missing 18+ verify if 18+ verify instance

